      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se origine a spaces : uscita                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-ssm-dpm-cct-org    =    spaces
                     go to ssm-dpm-sub-cct-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Conteggio leading blanks in origine             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-ssm-dpm-cct-c01      .
           inspect   w-ssm-dpm-cct-org
                                      tallying w-ssm-dpm-cct-c01
                                   for leading spaces                 .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione 1. carattere significativo in o- *
      *              * rigine                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-ssm-dpm-cct-c01      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Conteggio trailing blanks in destinazione       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-ssm-dpm-cct-c02      .
           inspect   w-ssm-dpm-cct-dst
                                      tallying w-ssm-dpm-cct-c02
                                  for trailing spaces                 .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione indice per destinazione          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-ssm-dpm-cct-c02    =    40
                     move     01          to   w-ssm-dpm-cct-inx
           else      move     40          to   w-ssm-dpm-cct-inx
                     subtract w-ssm-dpm-cct-c02
                                          from w-ssm-dpm-cct-inx
                     add      02          to   w-ssm-dpm-cct-inx      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se indice oltre il massimo : uscita             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-ssm-dpm-cct-inx    >    40
                     go to ssm-dpm-sub-cct-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Concatenamento                                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-ssm-dpm-cct-org
                    (w-ssm-dpm-cct-c01 :) to   w-ssm-dpm-cct-dst
                                              (w-ssm-dpm-cct-inx :)   .
       ssm-dpm-sub-cct-999.
           exit.

